<plot>Although not as popular as some of Steven Spielberg's other films, 1941 was nevertheless an important step in the legendary director's developemnt. This documentary takes a look behind the scenes at the making of the 1979 comedy, with interviews of the cast and crew, as well as archive footage of John Belushi and the rest of the stars as they took part in this small piece of film history.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?573750</url></doc>
